Package it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.resourcecontainers

package it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.resourcecontainers
This package contains the implementation of the resource containers of Masters of Renaissance.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    ResourceContainerGroup
    This interface represents a group of resource containers.
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    ResourceContainer
    This interface represents a container of storable resources.
    ResourceContainerGeneralGroup
    This class represents a group of general replaceable resource containers.
    ResourceShelf
    This class represents a limited container of resources of a specific type.
    Shelf
    This class represents a finite container of resources of the same type.
    Strongbox
    This class represents an infinite container of resources.
    Warehouse
    This class represents a group of warehouse shelves of growing size.
    Warehouse.WarehouseShelf
    This class represents a shelf in a warehouse, that is a shelf that cannot contain a resource that is contained also in another shelf of the same warehouse.
